---
const brand = "JaiSellers Companies";
const title = "About";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title} — {brand}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Founder-led infrastructure studio building governance, funding, and narrative systems for mission-driven work." />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/site.css" />
  </head>
<main>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="kicker">About</p>
      <h1>Founder-led. Systems-first.</h1>
      
     <body>
    <header class="topbar">
      <a class="logo" href="/">{brand}</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/consulting">Consulting (JSC)</a>
        <a href="/design">Design</a>
        <a href="/jsi">JSI</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a class="nav-cta" href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
  <img src="/images/AboutMe.png" alt="Photo of Joshua Jai Sellers" style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 20px;" />

      <p style="margin-top:14px; max-width:76ch;">
        JaiSellers Companies operates at the seam where creativity, strategy, and advocacy meet—honoring legacy while
        building what’s next.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
    <main>
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="kicker">About</p>
          <h1>Founder-led. Systems-first.</h1>
          <p style="margin-top:14px; max-width:76ch;">
            JaiSellers Companies operates at the seam where creativity, strategy, and advocacy meet—honoring legacy while
            building what’s next. We turn vision into structure: governance, funding, and brand systems that hold.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>What we believe</h2>
          <div class="grid3" style="margin-top:18px;">
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Structure is care</h3>
              <p>Clear governance and operating rhythms protect people and missions—especially under stress.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Story must match reality</h3>
              <p>Messaging should reflect what you can actually deliver—and invite the right support.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Equity needs infrastructure</h3>
              <p>Justice work collapses without systems. We build the foundation so power can last.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container split">
          <div>
            <h2>How we work</h2>
            <p style="margin-top:10px; max-width:70ch;">
              We deliver templates, checklists, trackers, and a cadence your team can run without you. The goal is
              durability—not dependency.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="callout">
            <h3>Next step</h3>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;">If you’re ready to build something stable, book a consult.</p>
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact" style="margin-top:12px;">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {brand}</span>
        <span class="sep">•</span>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
